address2: Unit 3309, 33rd Floor Shun Tak Centre 168-200 Connaught Road
longBusinessSummary: Good Fellow Healthcare Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides general hospital services in the People's Republic of China and internationally. Its general hospital services include medical and surgical wards, and medical checkup and examination. The company operates general hospitals in Putain and Beijing. It also provides medical investment and hospital management services; and hospital consulting management. The company was formerly known as Hua Xia Healthcare Holdings Limited and changed its name to Good Fellow Healthcare Holdings Limited in February 2019. Good Fellow Healthcare Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Good Fellow Healthcare Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Solar Star Global Limited.
